\c 6
\p
\v 1 Ipapo Dhariyasi mambo wakaita mutemo; zvino vakanzvera muimba yemabhuku, paiva pakaiswa zvinokosha muBhabhironi\x + 5.17.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino kwakawanikwa paAkimeta, pamuzinda\x + 1 Makor. 29.1.\x* waiva mudunhu reMedhi\x + 2 Madz. 17.6.\x*, rugwaro rwakapetwa, uye marwuri maiva nechirangaridzo chakanyorwa seizvi:
\p
\v 3 Mugore rekutanga raKoreshi mambo, Koreshi mambo wakaita murairo: Imba yaMwari paJerusarema, imba ngaivakwe, nzvimbo pavanopa zvibairo, uye nheyo dzayo ngadziteiwe; urefu hwayo makubhiti makumi matanhatu, upamhi hwayo makubhiti makumi matanhatu;
\v 4 ive \add ne\add*misara mitatu yemabwe makuru, nemusara wematanda matsva; uye muripo wezvishandiswa ngaupiwe kubva muimba yamambo\x + 1 Madz. 6.36.\x*.
\v 5 Nemidziyowo yegoridhe nesirivha yeimba yaMwari, Nebhukadhinezari yaakabudisa patembere iri paJerusarema ndokuiuisa kuBhabhironi, ngaidzoswe, iuiswezve patembere iri paJerusarema, panzvimbo yayo, mugoisa muimba yaMwari\x + 1.7,8. 5.14.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Zvino, Tatenai mutongi mhiri kwerwizi, Shetari-Bhozinai\x + 5.3,6. 6.13.\x*, nevafambidzani venyu VaAfarisaki\x + 4.9.\x*, vari mhiri kwerwizi, ivai kure naikoko.
\v 7 Regai basa reimba iyi yaMwari; mutongi weVaJudha nevakuru veVaJudha ngavavake imba iyi yaMwari panzvimbo yayo.
\v 8 Uye mutemo unoitwa neni zvamuchaita kuvakuru veVaJudha ava pakuvakwa kweimba iyi yaMwari, kuti pafuma yamambo, pamutero\x + 7.26. 2 Makor. 1.11.\x* mhiri kwerwizi, muripo wezvinoshandiswa uchapiwa kuvarume ava nekukurumidza, kuti vasamira\x + 4.13.\x*.
\v 9 Uye zvinodikanwa, zviri zviviri nzombe diki, nemakondohwe, nemakwayana, zvezvipo zvinopiswa zvaMwari wekumatenga, gorosi, munyu, waini, nemafuta, zvichienderana nekureva kwevapristi vari paJerusarema, ngazvipiwe kwavari zuva nezuva pasina kushaya hanya;
\v 10 kuti vape zvibairo zvehwema hunotapira kuna Mwari wekumatenga, uye vachinyengeterera upenyu hwamambo nehwevanakomana vake\x + Jer. 29.7. 1 Tim. 2.2.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino mutemo wamiswa neni, kuti ani nani anoshandura shoko iri, danda ngaribviswe paimba yake, uye asimudzwa, ngaaroverwe pamusoro paro; neimba yake ngaiitwe dutu rendove nekuda kweizvozvi\x + Dhan. 2.5. 3.29. 2 Madz. 10.27.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino Mwari wakaita kuti zita rake rigarepo ngaaparadze mambo upi neupi kana vanhu vachaisa ruoko rwavo kushandura \add ne\add*kuparadza imba iyi yaMwari iri paJerusarema. Ini Dhariyasi ndakamisa mutemo; ngazviitwe nekukurumidza\x + 1 Madz. 9.3.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Ipapo Tatenai mutongi mhiri kwerwizi, Shetari-Bhozenayi, nevafambidzani vake, vakaita saizvozvo nekukurumidza zvichienderana neizvo Dhariyasi mambo zvaaiva atuma.
\v 14 Zvino vakuru veVaJudha vakavaka ndokubudirira kubudikidza nechiporofita chaHagai muporofita, naZekariya mwanakomana waIdho\x + 5.1,2.\x*. Zvino vakavaka ndokupedza zvichienderana nemutemo waMwari waIsraeri, uye zvichienderana nemutemo waKoreshi\x + 6.3. 1.1. 5.13.\x*, naDhariyasi\x + 6.12. 4.24.\x*, naAritakiserikisi mambo wePerisiya\x + 7.1.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino imba iyi yakapedzwa nezuva retatu remwedzi weAdhari raiva riri gore retanhatu rekutonga kwaDhariyasi mambo\x + Esi. 3.7,13. 8.12. 9.1,15,17,19,21. 13.6. 16.20.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Zvino vana vaIsraeri, vapristi, neVaRevhi, nevamwe vevana veutapwa vakaita kutsaurwa kweimba iyi yaMwari nemufaro\x + 1 Madz. 8.63. 2 Makor. 7.5.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino vakapa pakutsaurwa kweimba iyi yaMwari nzombe zana, makondohwe mazana maviri, makwayana mazana mana; uye nhongo dzembudzi gumi nembiri dziri chipo chezvivi chaIsraeri wose zvichienderana neuwandu hwemarudzi aIsraeri\x + 8.35.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino vakamisa vapristi pazvikamu zvavo\x + 2 Makor. 35.5. 1 Makor. 24.1.\x*, neVaRevhi pamapoka avo\x + 1 Makor. 23.6. 2 Makor. 35.10.\x*, pashumiro yaMwari iri paJerusarema, sezvazvakanyorwa pabhuku raMozisi\x + Num.. 3.6. 8.9.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Zvino vana veutapwa vakaita pasika neregumi nemana remwedzi wekutanga\x + Eki. 12.6. 2 Makor. 35.1.\x*.
\v 20 Nokuti vapristi neVaRevhi vaiva vazvinatsa pamwe, vese vavo vaiva vakachena\x + 2 Makor. 30.15. 35.11.\x*; zvino vakabaira pasika vana vese veutapwa nehama dzavo vapristi, naivo vamene\x + 2 Makor. 30.15. 35.11.\x*.
\v 21 Saizvozvo vana vaIsraeri avo vakadzoka pautapwa nevese vakazvitsaurira kwavari\x + 9.1. Neh. 10.28. Neh. 9.2. Eki. 12.48,49. Esi. 8.17. 9.27.\x* kubva pakusachena kwemarudzi epanyika kuti vatsvake Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri\x + 9.11.\x* vakadya.
\v 22 Zvino vakaita mutambo wechingwa chisina kuviriswa mazuva manomwe nemufaro, nokuti Jehovha waiva avafadza\x + Eki. 12.15. 13.6. 2 Makor. 30.21. 35.17.\x*, ndokutendeusira kwavari moyo\x + 7.27. Zvir. 21.1.\x* wamambo weAsiriya, kuti asimbise maoko avo pabasa reimba yaMwari, Mwari waIsraeri\x + Neh. 13.6.\x*.